</div>
    <div class="markdown level0 conceptual"></div>
    
      
        <div class="codewrapper">
          <pre><code class="lang-csharp hljs">public void Begin(SpriteSortMode sortMode = SpriteSortMode.Deferred, BlendState blendState = null, SamplerState samplerState = null, DepthStencilState depthStencilState = null, RasterizerState rasterizerState = null, Effect effect = null, Matrix? transformMatrix = default(Matrix? ))</code></pre>
